ltr / listtrigger             Lists triggers
 
   Format:
      ;ltr
               Lists all triggers belonging to current profiles
      ;ltr -w
               Lists all triggers associated with the current world 
      ;ltr -g
               Lists all triggers associated with the current guild
      ;ltr -r
               Lists all triggers associated with the current race
      ;ltr -c
               Lists all triggers associated with the current character
      ;ltr -x <category>
               Lists all triggers belonging to the current custom profile
                  derived from the category (template) <category>
      ;ltr -d <prof>
               Lists all triggers belonging to the profile <prof>
      ;ltr -i
               Lists all active trigger interfaces
 
   User commands:
      ltr / listtrig / listtrigger
